{"tid":1253229,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"science：支 那 公 民 誠 信 全 球 最 低","createTime":"2019-06-23T12:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T16:34:16.000Z","uid":139484,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e3f2179b70bcef178eace63eb8ccb167443659","tid":1253229,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:43:08.000Z","msg":"《Science》今天發表論文《世界各地的公民誠信》，講四位科學家在 40 個國家的 355 個城市故意丟下錢包，看有多少人聯繫失主。 排名最前的五個國家為瑞士、挪威、荷蘭、丹麥、瑞典，都有 70 &ndash; 80% 的人聯繫失主。 中國則在一組實驗中排名最末，另一組實驗中排名倒數第五，只有 8% &ndash; 20% 的人聯繫失主（見圖一）。<br />\n<br />\n 具體實驗過程如下：論文作者選擇每個國家不緊挨著的幾個大城市（在中國他們選的是北京、上海、廣州、深圳、天津、西安、杭州、成都），請研究助理去鬧市區 的公共場所（例如銀行、博物館），把一個透明錢夾交給前台工作人員（見圖二），說他撿到一個別人遺失的錢夾，但他現在趕時間，希望前台工作人員能幫忙處理 。<br />\n<br />\n 錢夾裡有一些錢、一把鑰匙、三張相同的名片和一張購物清單。 錢是根據各國物價調整過的 13 美元。 在中國，這個數字是 49 人民幣。 名片上的名字選取每個國家最常見的男性名字，中國是 Chang Wei、Li Qiang、Wang Lei。 職務寫的是&ldquo;軟件開發&rdquo;，還留了郵箱。 購物清單寫的是各國常見食物，中國是礦泉水、包子、方便麵和蘋果。<br />\n<br />\n 研究人員在每個名片上留的郵箱地址都不同，實驗後 100 天內觀察了是否有人給該電郵地址寫信。<br />\n<br />\n 研究人員還同時&ldquo;遺失&rdquo;了一組裡面沒有錢、只有名片、鑰匙和購物清單的錢夾，結果每個國家聯繫失主的比例相較&ldquo;有錢的錢夾&rdquo;那組都更低。 這個結論也很有趣，因為在研究人員進行的網絡調查中，人們普遍猜測&ldquo;有錢的錢夾&rdquo;遺失後，失主被聯繫的概率更低。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rFJ3SD4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFJ3SD4.png&h=854cc513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇吓啲支那人點兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gEww1Ap.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgEww1Ap.png&h=04d2fb4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇理由咁低喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定係你唔合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那公民誠信最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab189809a21d2eb61eacf0257fdc69bb8290687","tid":1253229,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"咁少亞洲國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日韓台都冇"},{"pid":"11a7dca0412a5f14be66402a24059c21c44cd388","tid":1253229,"uid":191926,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"竟然有8% &ndash; 20%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b800808ab0860d4589a9a5f52aa4e18be9f030","tid":1253229,"uid":202412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"肯亞 迦納依啲黑人國家都高過世界強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e1aeb5db4e3862db0452f88e4ba07c069f69c8","tid":1253229,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b800808ab0860d4589a9a5f52aa4e18be9f030","tid":1253229,"uid":202412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"肯亞 迦納依啲黑人國家都高過世界強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"要點樣先會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627caf2f6d9fb6505e15932f19758c4e8f24fb0c","tid":1253229,"uid":17506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:20:20.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯仲高過英美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d7d5b56165d8054ef4e0dfa89ee1d29675c9e6","tid":1253229,"uid":113449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"大陸人唔興用電郵"},{"pid":"e0c3112ecff1963c8a4c87e2b888939a0df66b20","tid":1253229,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ee5cc7f12dc8d4ade6e796ca30bb284049e7a1","tid":1253229,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82e1ae